Package: catcheR
Type: Package
Title: Plasmid Library Sequencing Analysis for shRNA CATCHER Experiments
Version: 0.3.0
Date: 2026-05-18
Authors@R: person("Elisa", "Balmas",
    email = "elisa.balmas@unito.it",
    role  = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: End-to-end quality control and analysis of shRNA plasmid library
    sequencing data produced by the CATCHER / iPS2-seq protocol (HEDGe lab,
    UNITO). Provides R wrappers for plasmid library QC (step1QC, step2QC),
    10X single-cell barcode assignment (10Xcatch, 10XcatchQC), cell filtering
    (filtercatch), empty cell identification (nocatch), and barcode swap
    correction (sortcatch). All functions run natively without Docker.
